data.description: Gorgeous 3+Den Home featuring 2.5 Baths and Located Just 5 Minutes from Publix, CVS, and soon coming new McDonald's, 7-Eleven, Brickyard Express Car Wash etc. This Open floor plan Home is one you won't want to miss. A lot of upgrades are available, such as the beautiful white 42" wood kitchen cabinets, granite counter-tops, wood casing, tray ceilings in the living room and Master bedroom with floating crown molding and rope lighting, and Carrara Interior doors. Spacious Living area is a great place for spending time with your family. Clean front and back areas, paved long driveway. It is the ideal combination of comfort, modernity, and privacy. The house pad is elevated 42" above center crown of road, which eliminates the need for a lift station for the septic tank.
